                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ddf392de-e6f8-4554-8022-d354c85d92a4",
                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Argh! I've been slimed!",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2838b76f-029a-40d5-a1e1-d0c469236958",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "text": "Think of it as a big, sloppy kiss because you are so sweet.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0f94e509-2625-48c5-8e1f-6622fabfea9f",
                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "That's Shadow, the dog from the painting in Darla's Den. He's one of the protective spirits of the castle.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "dfb67ee3-169f-41f1-936b-59ded351a3b3",
                    "actorId": "98ea49aa-86cf-4fa9-9bd5-6aa2fe7c809d",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Vell, he protected me from supper - he licked my plate clean... if you overlook puddle of drool he left behind.",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e7622374-55ed-43f2-be1d-922598f5d96b",
                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I will be sooo glad when the Nights of the Dead are over. I don't like having ghosts hanging around everywhere I go.",
                    "emotion": "4",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0aa91e17-bfe5-49af-bc86-cbc604a4a18d",
                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "text": "The protective spirits like Shadow, Voodoo, and Leo are around all the time, you just can't always see them.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2c418e6b-76eb-45bb-a4e5-dbec9343d605",
                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "actorId2": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                    "text": "I really didn't want to know that, Thomas. Thank you very much.",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f4110065-3655-4942-a941-6d9991efb3be",
                    "actorId": "5ffe0a3d-d152-412f-bc75-480092ca6256",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This is unacceptable! How can anyone stand these ghosts around everywhere! ",
                    "emotion": "3",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7f1b189e-01d1-4377-84e3-1e5f76848124",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "text": "Clearly, Katie, you aren't the only one annoyed by the Ghosts.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "12a10559-2752-483b-ba50-df852c43347a",
                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Okay, so maybe they aren't all that bad. ",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0",
                    "notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.setTime",
                    "id": "69232ce7-7316-4e8d-b223-5ed6bfe1076f",
